Module Programming

Package org.hust.common.exception

  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    AlreadyRentBikeException
    This exception is throws when user try to rent bike when they have already rent a bike.
    HaveNotRentBikeException
    This exception is throws when user try to view current rented or return bike when they are not renting any.
    InternalServerErrorException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to internal server error.
    InvalidBarcodeException
    This exception is throws when user input an invalid barcode.
    InvalidCardException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to invalid card.
    InvalidFormatException
    This exception is throws when detect invalid format in user's input.
    InvalidIdException
    This exception is throws when invalid id is used in code.
    InvalidIdFormatException
    This exception is throws when user input id in the wrong format.
    InvalidLocationException
    This exception is throws when user try to find a station at a location that have no station in there.
    InvalidLocationFormatException
    This exception is throws when user input station's location in a wrong format.
    InvalidTransactionAmountException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to invalid transaction amount.
    InvalidVersionException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to invalid version.
    NotEnoughBalanceException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to not enough balance.
    NotEnoughTransactionInfoException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to not enough transaction info.
    PaymentException
    This exception is throws when receive error when making payment transaction with known reasons.
    SuspiciousTransactionException
    This exception is throws when receive response from interbank with the error code correspond to suspicious transaction.
    UnrecognizedException
    This exception is throws when receive error when making payment transaction with unknown reasons.
